<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recu Paiement - Commande #{{ commande.idCommande }}</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --ink: #0f172a;
            --muted: #475569;
            --brand-a: #0f766e;
            --brand-b: #16a34a;
            --line: #dbeafe;
            --paper: #ffffff;
            --bg: #f0fdfa;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", "Open Sans", sans-serif;
            color: var(--ink);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% -10%, #ccfbf1 0%, #f8fafc 55%, #eef2ff 100%);
            padding: 28px 14px;
        }

        .page {
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .toolbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .btn {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #fff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-a) 0%, var(--brand-b) 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 18px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #334155;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .receipt {
            background: var(--paper);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
            position: relative;
        }

        .receipt::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(34,197,94,0.05) 0%, rgba(20,184,166,0.02) 45%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 70%);
        }

        .hero {
            padding: 24px;
            color: #f0fdfa;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #115e59 0%, #15803d 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: flex-start;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            right: -95px;
            top: -85px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,.2) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 72%);
        }

        .brand-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.95);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);
            object-fit: contain;
            padding: 6px;
        }

        .brand-name {
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: .04em;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #ecfeff;
            opacity: 0.97;
        }

        .brand-tagline {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(236,254,255,.9);
            letter-spacing: .04em;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 6px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .paid-pill {
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            white-space: nowrap;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 22px;
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .card {
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 14px;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .label {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: .05em;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .value {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0b3b2e;
        }

        .total {
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .total strong {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #166534;
        }

        .foot {
            padding: 16px 22px 24px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .no-print { display: block; }

        @media (max-width: 740px) {
            .hero { flex-direction: column; }
            .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .total { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
        }

        @media print {
            body {
                background: #fff;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .page {
                max-width: none;
                margin: 0;
            }
            .receipt {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .no-print { display: none !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
    <div class="toolbar no-print">
        <button class="btn" type="button" onclick="window.print()">Imprimer</button>
        {% if is_download|default(false) == false %}
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ path('app_commande_show', {id: commande.idCommande}) }}" style="text-decoration:none;">Retour</a>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <section class="receipt">
        <header class="hero">
            <div>
                <div class="brand-row">
                    <img class="brand-logo" src="{{ receipt_logo_data_uri|default(asset('assets/img/logo.png')) }}" alt="Logo EL FIRMA">
                    <div>
                        <div class="brand-name">EL FIRMA</div>
                        <p class="brand-tagline">Agriculture durable et intelligente</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h1>Recu de Paiement</h1>
                <p>Commande #{{ commande.idCommande }} - EL FIRMA</p>
            </div>
            <div class="paid-pill">Paiement confirme</div>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="label">Client</div>
                    <div class="value">{{ commande.nomClient }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="label">Date paiement</div>
                    <div class="value">{{ commande.dateCommande ? commande.dateCommande|date('d/m/Y H:i') : '-' }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="label">Adresse livraison</div>
                    <div class="value">{{ commande.adresseLivraison ?: 'Non renseignee' }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="label">Mode paiement</div>
                    <div class="value">{{ commande.modePaiement }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="label">Statut paiement</div>
                    <div class="value">{{ commande.statutPaiement }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="label">Produit</div>
                    <div class="value">{{ commande.produit ? commande.produit.nom : 'Produit supprime' }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="total">
                <div>
                    <div class="label">Montant regle</div>
                    <div class="value">Quantite: {{ commande.quantite }}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: right;">
                    <strong>{{ commande.prixTotal|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} DT</strong>
                    {% if tnd_to_eur_rate is not null %}
                        <div style="margin-top: 6px; color: #0f766e; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px;">~ {{ (commande.prixTotal * tnd_to_eur_rate)|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} EUR</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="foot">
            Ce document sert de preuve de paiement de la commande. Vous pouvez l'imprimer en cliquant sur le bouton Imprimer.
        </footer>
    </section>
</div>
</body>
</html>
